itunes:summary:
Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez star in HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning - this episode aired on 7/22. 

Ebro and the crew discuss flooding in China and the American wildfires (12), Laura Stylez has her patented Flashing Lights segments (17 & 1:16), and the Gurus guide you through the twists and turns of life (1:09). Are you ready for new Kanye?
